Titolo: Polanie II

Anno: 2003

Descrizione: Polanie II , also known as KnightShift and Once Upon a Knight, is a real-time strategy and role-playing video game hybrid developed by Reality Pump Studios and released by Topware Interactive for the PC Windows and OS X in 2003. The game is a follow-up to  Polanie, published by USER in 1996. KnightShift (Director's Cut Special Edition) was released for Windows later in 2003.